items.title: On Donald Trump’s Virtues
items.description: Trump’s many and well-known vices should not leave us unable to see that the man also has his virtues.

items.title: Michael Mann Finally Goes Away
items.description: The climate scientist tried to trample our free-speech rights, and failed.

items.title: Trump Should Back Doctor Visits for Abortion Drugs
items.description: Joe Biden discarded a policy that had stood for nearly all of Barack Obama’s presidency and all of Trump’s first term.

items.title: Yes, Test Our Nukes
items.description: It would represent an advance for the U.S. nuclear deterrent and a victory of common sense over superstition.

items.title: Trump’s Cease-Fire with China
items.description: It was probably the best that could be expected from the bad options.
